PrecisRe-appointment of PIERRE TREMBLAY, of Ste-Foy, Quebec, for a term of two years, effective March 12, 2000, as a Canadian representative to the Council of the North Atlantic Salmon Conservation Organization; to the North American Commission of the North Atlantic Salmon Conservation Organization; and to the West Greenland Commission of the North Atlantic Salmon Conservation Organization.

precis:
Re-appointment of PIERRE TREMBLAY, of Ste-Foy, Quebec, for a term of two
years, effective March 12, 2000, as a Canadian representative to the
Council of the North Atlantic Salmon Conservation Organization; to the
North American Commission of the North Atlantic Salmon Conservation
Organization; and to the West Greenland Commission of the North Atlantic
Salmon Conservation Organization.
